{{Infobox weapon
| used_by = [[Shiva]]
| name = Pinaka
| image = Rama breaking the bow to win Sita as wife.jpg
| caption = Rama breaking Shiva's Dhanush (bow) to win Sita as wife
| image_size = 300px
| type = [[Bow and arrow|Bow]]
